The paper focuses on cybersecurity education and awareness for small- and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs), which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY). The paper also discusses best practices and recommendations for developing a high-level program, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and education and training (cs.ET). Additionally, the paper mentions the importance of building awareness and education, which could fall under human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
